rows.label: tlk400904_msg0001
rows.name:
Sorry, but I don't do small talk with
people who aren't paying customers.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0002
rows.name:
Maybe if you bought something,
I'd be more willing to chat.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, if you're not paying,
I'm not talking!

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0006
rows.name:
Thanks for your custom!
And whaddaya know, I think
I just remembered!

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0007
rows.name:
You're looking for an old bloke
by the name of Timell.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0008
rows.name:
He's in the business of transporting
Black Ash and other minerals mined
in Superbia.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0009
rows.name:
Right now, you'll probably find
him at the Turbine Tower, just
across Midorl Bridge.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0010
rows.name:
Be careful if you're going to
meet him, though.
